Provenance
------------------------------------------------------------------------
These files are a curated subset (~12 chapters, one representative chapter
per web-applicable top-level section) of etc/doc/tutorial/ from the pinned
upstream commit above. They are a build INPUT to tools/ingest-tutorial.ts,
which bakes them into src/tutorial/tutorialData.ts. The raw markdown is
never shipped to the runtime. Re-running the ingester against this pinned
content is deterministic.
